com.example.mdbook

Class Patient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mdbook.User
      • com.example.mdbook.Patient

  • class Patient
extends User
    Extends User into the patient class. Adds a problem list. Provides methods for adding and removing problems. If a problem needs to be updated, the actual problem object should be updated, not replaced with an updated copy. Hence no updateProblem() method.
    Version:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Noah Burghardt
    See Also:
    Problem, User
